text: We chanced upon this quirky little karaoke bar. After a beer or 3 we worked out how to get involved, and gave the locals some dodgy duets. Lina the owner introduced herself and bought us a drink to celebrate our honeymoon. Overall a fairly surreal evening but lots of fun.
Great place for late night pool and drinks.

A small and lively pub located at Odean Katong mall. The pool table tends to get in the way.
